            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20we%20become%20Christians%2C%20many%20of%20us%20think%20we%20are%20%22good.%22%20The%20Word%20of%20God%2C%20however%2C%20clearly%20states%20the%20contrary.%20At%20one%20time%2C%20all%20of%20us%20%22were%20foolish%20and%20disobedient.%20We%20were%20misled%20by%20others%20and%20became%20slaves%20to%20many%20wicked%20desires%20and%20evil%20pleasures.%20Our%20lives%20were%20full%20of%20evil%20and%20envy.%20We%20hated%20others%2C%20and%20they%20hated%20us%22%20(Titus%203%3A3).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20His%20kindness%20and%20love%2C%20God%20saved%20us%2C%20washed%20us%20in%20His%20blood%2C%20and%20renewed%20us%20in%20the%20Holy%20Spirit.%20His%20goodness%20to%20us%20made%20us%20good.%20Now%2C%20because%20of%20that%20goodness%20living%20in%20us%2C%20we%20devote%20our%20lives%20to%20doing%20what%20is%20good%20(v.%208).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EDoing%20good%20includes%20submitting%20to%20those%20in%20authority%2C%20and%20living%20an%20obedient%2C%20gentle%2C%20humble%2C%20and%20peaceable%20life%20(v.%202).%20As%20we%20follow%20these%20guidelines%2C%20we%20will%20live%20productive%20lives%2C%20devoting%20ourselves%20to%20providing%20for%20daily%20necessities%20and%20the%20needs%20of%20others%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(v.%2014).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20central%20theme%20of%20the%20Psalms%20is%20the%20goodness%20of%20the%20Lord.%20Psalm%20100%3A5%20puts%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%22For%20the%20Lord%20is%20good.%20His%20unfailing%20love%20continues%20forever%2C%20and%20his%20faithfulness%20continues%20to%20each%20generation.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELet%20us%20enjoy%20His%20goodness%20today%20and%20rejoice%20that%20He%20has%20changed%20us%20into%20someone%20%22good.%22%20God%20is%20good%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20so%20should%20we%20be!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
